metadata.name: A8 Wolf Breeding
metadata.description:
This deed entitles the holder to one (1) breeding session with InfiniGods' Alpha 8 Wolf (#12890) in Wolf Game. 

TERMS—

– This token must be burned to redeem.  
– Use is subject to Wolf availability (breeding consumes energy and must be recharged).  
– The holder is responsible for the Den fee, CHOPS, and providing a second Wolf to breed with.
